the entry, and fires `OnConsoleEntryCreated`/`OnConsoleEntryDeleted` ICONTEXT callbacks. Disk layout: `<TemporaryPath>/Console/<persona>/<fp-2>/<fp-22>/<container>-NNNN.log`. Entry serialization: `ToJson()` writes epoch seconds as `"stamp"` (double), `FromJson()` reconstitutes `system_clock::time_point`. `FormatStamp()` produces `HH:MM:SS.mmm`. `MessageParts()` parses JSON arrays for structured display. Notifications: `OnConsoleStreamCreated/Deleted`, `OnConsoleEntryCreated/Deleted` via ICONTEXT. Thread safety: `m_mxConsole` (recursive_mutex) on CONSOLE, `m_mxStream` (recursive_mutex) per STREAM, `m_mutex` (recursive_mutex) per BLOCK. Public header: `include/Console.h`. Private header: `Console.h` (declares `ICONSOLE_IMPL` and `BLOCK`). Implementation: `Console.cpp`, `Stream.cpp`, `Block.cpp`, `Entry.cpp`. See `Console.md` for full documentation. **Build status: compiles and links clean, 44/44 console tests pass. ~90% complete.** Not yet implemented: WASM host function wiring, null-CID engine stream, inspector UI, stream-level entry aggregation, block rotation on config change. | Active |
