POSITOR`, `SCRUB`, `FETCH`, `C`) call `Join()` in their destructors. `Ready(bool bResult = true)` signals the initializing thread that startup is complete. `IsShutdown()` returns the shutdown flag. Non-copyable, non-movable. See **THREAD / CONTROL / AGENT wait and shutdown contract** under Design Principles. |
