**Naming note:** The concrete renderer class is `renderer::ANARI_RENDERER`. The ANARI SDK's `ANARI_*` enum constants (e.g. `ANARI_RENDERER`, `ANARI_CAMERA`) live in the global namespace, so scoping ours inside `renderer` avoids collision without needing a backend-specific class name.

### Test Suites (unified `SneezeTest` executable)

